      <procstep>
        <procdesc>Dataset copied from the cd obtained from Washington, DC 2005

The points were identified from public records (including published maps and the District of Columbia's Inventory of Historic Sites) and heads-up digitized using the 1995 orthophotographs. They were not fit to the planimetrics, which were not available at the time of creation. Attribute data was provided by public records.

All DC GIS data is stored and exported in Maryland State Plane coordinates NAD 83 meters.</procdesc>
